## Run the Project

1. Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone <your_repo_url>
cd backend-ecommerce
npm install

set your .env:
PORT=5000
DB_URL=<your_mongodb_uri>
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=<cloud_name>
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=<api_key>
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=<api_secret>

run the project:
npm run dev



